OnDesktop Mouse1 :HideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse2 :WorkspaceMenu
OnDesktop Mouse3 :RootMenu
OnDesktop Mouse4 :NextWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse5 :PrevWorkspace

Mod1 Tab :NextWindow
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow

Mod1 Control l :ExecCommand xscreensaver-command -lock
Mod1 F2 :ExecCommand fbrun
F10 :Maximize
Mod1 F9 :Minimize

Mod1 Control Return :ExecCommand gnome-terminal 

Mod1 Control Left :PrevWorkspace
Mod1 Control Right :NextWorkspace
Mod1 Control Up :PrevWorkspace 2
Mod1 Control Down :NextWorkspace 2

Mod1 Control Shift Left :TakeToPrevWorkspace 1  
Mod1 Control Shift Right :TakeToNextWorkspace 1
Mod1 Control Shift Up :TakeToPrevWorkspace 2
Mod1 Control Shift Down :TakeToNextWorkspace 2

